parameters:
Hehehe... It feels like I have the beach all to myself. Well, there
are a few people here and there...

But even though there are few people, being completely exposed is a
bit...
T-That... isn't a swimsuit, right? It's a bit lewd...

……By the way, are you not mistaking this place for a public bath or
something?
Ugh, whoa...!? Is this really a beach...?
There's... no one here... As expected, it's impossible now...
There are no playmates here except for crabs.
There's no one here... As expected, it's impossible now...

You're dressed pretty strangely... You're not planning on wearing that
as a swimsuit, are you?
There's no one here... As expected, it's impossible now...

I thought there was no one here, but there's a cute girl. Nice...
wanna play?
There's... no one here... As expected, it's impossible now...
There are no playmates here except for crabs.

The beach is currently dangerous. At least you need to have the
qualification of a \c[6]Explorer\c[0] to pass.
……Or rather, even before that, it's not okay just because it's a beach.
Oh, you're an explorer. Be careful ahead because monsters will appear.

……By the way, you don't have permission to walk around dressed like
that, right? Put on proper clothes, hey.
我が眷属をつんつんせし不躾なる人間よ……。
全てのカニを統べるものとして今こそ天罰を下そう……。
W-What was that voice just now...?
